âœ¨ Supports both **CLI (Command Line Interface)** and **GUI (Tkinter)**  
âœ¨ Built with **Pillow** (image handling) and **Stepic** (steganography functions)  
âœ¨ Works on **Linux, Windows, and MacOS**  
âœ¨ Simple **GUI buttons** for Encode and Decode  
âœ¨ Output images look **exactly like the original** (no visible distortion)  

